### Webhook Examples for Pallet Bot WhatsApp

### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Start - First message (creates session)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "oi"
}

### 2. Global command - novo
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "novo"
}

### 3. Menu - Choose option 1 (Planta real)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "buttonReply": "1"
}

### 4. Menu - Choose option 2 (Medidas digitadas)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "buttonReply": "2"
}

### 5. WAIT_PLANT_IMAGE - Send image
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "media": {
    "type": "image",
    "id": "image_12345"
  }
}

### 6. WAIT_LENGTH - Enter length
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "12000"
}

### 7. WAIT_WIDTH - Enter width
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "10000"
}

### 8. WAIT_CORRIDOR - Enter corridor width
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "3000"
}

### 9. WAIT_CAPACITY - Enter capacity
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "2000"
}

### 10. CHOOSE_HEIGHT_MODE - Choose DIRECT
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "buttonReply": "DIRECT"
}

### 11. CHOOSE_HEIGHT_MODE - Choose CALC
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "buttonReply": "CALC"
}

### 12. WAIT_HEIGHT_DIRECT - Enter height
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "5000"
}

### 13. WAIT_LOAD_HEIGHT - Enter load height
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "1500"
}

### 14. WAIT_LEVELS - Enter levels
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "5"
}

### 15. WAIT_EXTRAS_GUARD_RAIL - Choose guard rail
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "buttonReply": "ambos"
}

### 16. SUMMARY_CONFIRM - Generate document
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "buttonReply": "GERAR"
}

### 17. Global command - voltar
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "voltar"
}

### 18. Global command - cancelar
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "cancelar"
}

### 19. Global command - status
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "status"
}

### 20. Validation error - Invalid length (too small)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "400"
}

### 21. Validation error - Invalid length (too large)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "250000"
}

### 22. Validation error - Invalid corridor
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "500"
}

### 23. Validation error - Invalid capacity
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "50"
}

### 24. Validation error - Invalid levels
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "from": "5511999999999",
  "text": "15"
